                        Our work is building a safer, healthier, more prosperous world for people in developing countries and in the
                        UK too. This site shows in detail the international development programmes led by the Foreign, Commonwealth
                        and Development Office (FCDO), other government departments and partners.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="/new_layout_assets/assets/images/uk-aid_logo-w.png" alt="UK aid from the British people"
                         class="app-banner__image">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
